<div style="text-align:center;">
<p style="color: darkorchid;font-size:20pt;font-family: 'Fira Sans Condensed', sans-serif; text-shadow: 2px 2px 2px grey;">Hola {{ usuario }} !</p>
<a href="/admin/login/logout"><button type="submit" style="width: 60px;height: 30px;background-color: darkorchid;color: white;font-family: 'Saira', sans-serif;border-radius: 50px;font-size:10pt;">Salir</button></a>
